casebody.data:
Nordlinger, Respondent, v. Levine, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 13, 1891.) Appeal from fifth district court. Action by Henry Nordlinger against Morris Levine.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff, J.

Mr. Goodhart, for appellant. Goggenheimer & Untermeyer, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
